Author: luplum
Text: > this is how normal people think, right?   Me, not a normal person at all: Yes! :)  Sometimes it feels like I have two people in my head, I swear. A crazy one and an insane one.  Insane: It's fine. I just need to reach my GW and then I'll stop.   Sane: Your GW is too underweight. People are already saying you're too thin.   Insane: That's just because they're used to seeing me bigger.   Sane: You're not going to stop at your GW. Most likely you won't even reach it, you'll become too hungry and spiral into B/P.   Insane: I'll reach it. Then I'll be happy, and I'll only need to maintain.   Sane: That's what you said about the last 3 kilos, but then you just decided on a new GW.   Insane: It's fine:)
